n不同顏色同線條代表唔同日子，顏色重疊愈多會有愈多殘留物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 因為資料不齊，請大家TG報料（@woohooha) 及提出意見，會盡力keep update<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86f95085a0ff333eb9f605c54811e9216b7e2be","tid":1727771,"uid":194255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCNQLK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCNQLK9.jpg&h=5053d688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCxJmiv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCxJmiv.jpg&h=89a11b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfrom 文宣gp<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5be17c953ddda23955c7adbde590c3b3f39da6","tid":1727771,"uid":153268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"P for push!!"},{"pid":"efc8753572b84ed6154e079984c0941319d83aea","tid":1727771,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4af543a5a1ec5ddcd328f484449e7f024aba1e0d","tid":1727771,"uid":153268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"78b3a8de27d7a7478878eecdf98efdff4fe4ae40","tid":1727771,"uid":268656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"926d268e8d9a3dd32dde72fa33e901dc659a626b","tid":1727771,"uid":194255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"初次嘗試整香港毒氣地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因為資料關係，暫時只整咗最近五日，請