r。可以試下click右上角expand screen icon，都有可能入到google map。（或者喺IPAD，電腦開，完全冇問題）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 入咗去可以&ldquo;view map legend&rdquo;，選擇想睇的日期。以日期排的原因係方便大家睇近幾日有冇放過彈，越遠的日子殘留物越少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不同顏色同線條代表唔同日子，顏色重疊愈多會有愈多殘留物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 因為資料不齊，請大家TG報料（@woohooha) 及提出意見，會盡力keep update<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝"},{"pid":"9f7412ee9fe75dd33bbc9b9bbe7731ca1eda6232","tid":1727771,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1e82c1a0fadd6750a980e05f8359f86fd2dd6c","tid":1727771,"uid":194255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb107e467520b1ba853a8e49983aab885cbb36a","tid":1727771,"uid":56699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37484bb88fbdfe519247574abbd39a98ab232