ssets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因為資料關係，暫時只整咗最近五日，請見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n使用説明：<br />\n1. 開link: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fembed%3Fmid%3D1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok%26ll%3D22.382581894986814%252C114.10570435%26z%3D11&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=e6268bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1J0xABJYyqeY7V9BBAd-Q_ZCY3Mn22wok&amp;ll=22.382581894986814%2C114.10570435&amp;z=11</a><br />\n2. 測試過，會直接跳入google map<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 如果未能直接入google map，喺部分android 機試過唔得，一開入去係internet browser。可以試下click右上角expand screen icon，都有可能入到google map。（或者喺IPAD，電腦開，完全冇問題）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 入咗去可以&ldquo;view map legend&rdquo;，選擇想睇的日期。以日期排的原因係方便大家睇近幾日有冇放過彈，越遠的日子殘留物越少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不同顏色同線條代表唔同日子，顏色重疊愈多會有愈多殘留物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 因為資料不齊，請大家TG報料（@woohooha) 及提出意見，會盡力keep update<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"要有英文version<br />\n比外傭<br />\n外國人<br />\n遊客"},{"pid":"ac3458bd6c74501d4a3491b7c5f927e18f866446","tid":1727771,"uid":